author: Rosie
name: Applications
install_msg:
Thank you for installing the Applications cog!
Do `[p]help Applications` to get the list of commands and their description. If you want to help translate, go to my [crowdin](<https://crowdin.com/project/Star-Cogs>)
If you like my work, [donate me!](<https://ko-fi.com/starcogs>)

This cog provides a comprehensive application system for your Discord server, allowing you to create custom application types, manage applications, and review them efficiently!
end_user_data_statement: This cog stores user IDs and application responses for the purpose of managing applications. This data is only stored within the bot's configuration and is not shared with external services.
